The paper discusses the privacy protection problem in the edge-cloud system running DNN models, which involves both computer security (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG) aspects. The paper also mentions computer vision (cs.CV) and system and control (cs.SY) as related fields. Additionally, the paper discusses the computation demand and resource limitations, which falls under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
